  "description": "Process Data from Wearable Light Loggers and Optical Radiation Dosimeters. \n\nImport, processing, validation, and visualization of personal light exposure measurement data from wearable devices. The package for R statistical software implements features such as the import of data and metadata files, conversion of common file formats, validation of light logging data, verification of crucial metadata, calculation of common parameters, and semi-automated analysis and visualization.",
